CARBON FOOTPRINT DROP-IN CODE FOR EY CLOUD DASHBOARD
----------------------------------------------------
By Brighter Planet, For Our Favorite PaaS

Check out doc/popup.png for how it should look.

We're basing it off how you guys do the HTTP Monitoring lightbox in More Options.

What you'll find in this repo:
* 1 route /environments/X/carbon_footprint
* 1 controller action
* 2 view files

The javascript makes an API call like: (amazon c1.xlarge instance running for a month in us-east-1a)

http://carbon.brighterplanet.com/computations.json?carrier=amazon&carrier_instance_class=c1.xlarge&duration=2700000&carrier_region=us-east-1a

You can also see a pretty methodology document for this same calculation by requesting HTML format:

http://carbon.brighterplanet.com/computations.html?carrier=amazon&carrier_instance_class=c1.xlarge&duration=2700000&carrier_region=us-east-1a

Any questions, please call Andy (x302) or Seamus (x305) on our main line (802) 458-0441.
